data.title: Royal Netherlands Air Force (RNAF) AH-64E Apache load
data.meta_description: The first of two Royal Netherlands Air Force (RNAF) AH-64E Apache helicopters is loaded onto a C-17 aircraft for transport to Woensdrecht Air Base, Netherlands. The Version 6 Apaches were delivered to the RNAF on December 7, and are the initial two of 28 upgraded helicopters the Netherlands will receive by 2025.  (courtesy photo)
